            <abstract>
                <p>This miracle seems to exist in at least two versions, of which <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5003MiracleJonahWife">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of Jonah, his wife and another woman</ref> mentions the names of the protagonists and places, 
                    while they remain unnamed in <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3868Miracle">Miracle of Mary: How a man forsook his wife and loved another woman who was a worshipper of the Virgin Mary and repented</ref>. This is the general ID to be used in cases where no version can be identified.</p>
